name: atx-osg
body:
### Austin Open Source GIS
Austin Open Source GIS (_atx-osg_) is for people interested in learning about, using, developing, or promoting open source tools in the field of Geographic Information Systems. Members of atx-osg are GIS professionals, developers and students passionate about generating more open source discussion in the local geospatial community. Membership is free and open to all.

### Join atx-osg

You can find us on Meetup: http://www.meetup.com/atx-osg/

Join our mailing list to keep up with the latest news & discussions:

http://groups.google.com/group/atx-osg/subscribe

### Meetups

Happy hours are held on the second Monday of every month.

Workshops & tech event schedules vary: check the Meetup page or the mailing list for details.
